    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Asset Catalog DATALAKE SYNC\n\nPulls full asset catalog from a datalake on a schedule.\nNO filtering at ingest, consumers filter at query time.\nUPSERT strategy: match on asset_id, update or insert as needed.\n\nOutputs to: asset_catalog (n8n data table)\nReaders: Asset Catalog Query Form, Asset Catalog Query API\n\nHandles large binaries via this.helpers.getBinaryDataBuffer().\nFixes upstream typo: service_grou, service_groue.\n\nOwner: [Owner]",
        "height": 384,
        "width": 624
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        432,
        -432
