      "parameters": {
        "content": "## STEP 2: POLL UNTIL READY\nDatalake generates CSV asynchronously.\nLoop: wait → poll status → if \"Success\", proceed. Otherwise loop.\nOn error → falls through to Log Datalake Error branch.",
